  "announcement_github_body": "## Install moove 0.4.6\n\n### Install prebuilt binaries via Homebrew\n\n```sh\nbrew install urin/moove/moove\n```\n\n## Download moove 0.4.6\n\n|  File  | Platform | Checksum |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| [moove-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.gz](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.gz) | Apple Silicon macOS | [checksum](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.gz.sha256) |\n| [moove-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip) | x64 Windows | [checksum](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip.sha256) |\n| [moove-aarch64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-aarch64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz) | ARM64 MUSL Linux | [checksum](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-aarch64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz.sha256) |\n| [moove-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz) | x64 MUSL Linux | [checksum](https://github.com/urin/moove/releases/download/v0.4.6/moove-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz.sha256) |\n\n## Verifying GitHub Artifact Attestations\n\nThe artifacts in this release have attestations generated with GitHub Artifact Attestations. These can be verified by using the [GitHub CLI](https://cli.github.com/manual/gh_attestation_verify):\n```sh\ngh attestation verify <file-path of downloaded artifact> --repo urin/moove\n```\n\nYou can also download the attestation from [GitHub](https://github.com/urin/moove/attestations) and verify against that directly:\n```sh\ngh attestation verify <file-path of downloaded artifact> --bundle <file-path of downloaded attestation>\n```\n\n",
